column2: SELECT TOP # p.ra, p.dec, p.run, p.rerun, p.camCol, p.field, p.obj, IS# (s.plate, #) as plate, IS# (s.mjd, #) as mjd, IS# (s.fiberid, #) as fiberid, q.fieldQall as quality FROM BESTDR7..PhotoObj AS p LEFT OUTER JOIN BESTDR7..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID JOIN RunQA AS q ON q.fieldid = p.fieldid JOIN #x AS x ON x.objID = p.objID JOIN #upload AS u ON u.up_id = x.up_id WHERE (q.fieldQall > = #) AND (p.type = # OR p.type = #) ORDER BY x.up_id
